Script,DOPIROPITest
window.currentPBSScenario = 'DOPIROPITest';
window.currentPBSScenarioFilename = 'DOPI_ROPI_Test';
console.log('PBS: Logging scenario selection for DOPIROPITest');
fetch('https://bba.harmonicsystems.com/api/scenario/select', {
    method: 'POST',
    headers: {
        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
        'X-Client-Version': '1.0.0'
    },
    body: JSON.stringify({
        scenario: 'DOPIROPITest',
        user: whoAmI() || 'anonymous'
    })
}).then(function(r){ console.log('PBS: Server response', r.status); }).catch(function(e){ console.log('PBS: Fetch error', e); });
setDealerCode(`

/*
convention-card-ns: 21GF-DEFAULT
convention-card-ew: 21GF-DEFAULT
auction-filter: (4N +[X5]|4N\n[X5])
*/
# DOPI-ROPI 1-Level-Overcall Test
dealer north

##### Imported Script -- GIB 1 Notrump #####

ntP = hcp(north) + shape(north,5xxx+x5xx)
nt1 = shape(north, any 5332+any 4432+any 4333) and hcp(north)>14 and ntP<18
nt2 = shape(north, any 5422-5xxx-x5xx-4xxx) and hcp(north)>14 and hcp(north)<17
gibNT = nt1 or nt2

### End of GIB 1 Notrump ###

# N has a standard 1-of-a-suit opening (not 1NT)
nOpens = hcp(north)>=12 and hcp(north)<=21 and not gibNT

# N/S in slam zone
slamZone = hcp(south)>=12 and (hcp(north)+hcp(south))>=28

# E/W have 11+ card major fit, both 5+
ewHearts11 = hearts(west)+hearts(east)>=11 and hearts(west)>=5 and hearts(east)>=5
ewSpades11 = spades(west)+spades(east)>=11 and spades(west)>=5 and spades(east)>=5

# N's opening suit must be lower-ranking than E/W's fit suit
# Heart fit: N opens 1C or 1D (no 5+ major)
# Spade fit: N opens 1C, 1D, or 1H (no 5+ spades)
heartScenario = ewHearts11 and
                (clubs(north)>=5 or diamonds(north)>=5) and
                hearts(north)<5 and spades(north)<5
spadeScenario = ewSpades11 and
                (clubs(north)>=5 or diamonds(north)>=5 or hearts(north)>=5) and
                spades(north)<5
scenario = heartScenario or spadeScenario

# E/W combined HCP modest (overcall + raise, not their own opening)
ewModest = (hcp(west)+hcp(east))<=22

nOpens and slamZone and scenario and ewModest

action printoneline,
average "hcp north     " hcp(north),
average "hcp south     " hcp(south),
average "hcp e+w       " (hcp(east)+hcp(west)),
average "ew hearts fit " 100 * ewHearts11,
average "ew spades fit " 100 * ewSpades11,
`, "N", true)
Script
Button,DOPI-ROPI Test (1-Level),\n\
--- DOPI-ROPI Test (1-level overcall variant，21GF-DEFAULT both sides)\n\
Diagnostic: E/W have an 11+ card major fit (5/6 or 6/5+); they start with a\n\
1-level overcall or weak-jump overcall. N opens a lower-ranking suit，N/S in\n\
slam zone. After N/S reach 4NT，do opponents bid 5-level，triggering\n\
DOPI/ROPI from N/S?\n\
%DOPIROPITest%,backgroundColor=lightpink
